'''''Old School RuneScape''''' is [[Jagex]]'s official term for a previous version of the ''RuneScape'' game that was introduced from the [[August 2007 Archive of RuneScape]], a backup of the ''RuneScape'' source code as it had been on [[10 August]] [[2007]]. It is also commonly referred to as '''OSRS''' or '''2007scape'''.

This version of the game was announced in a {{RSL|Update:2007 - Old School RuneScape... You Vote!|news post}} on {{RSL|13 February}} {{RSL|2013}}, which was followed by the opening of a poll to determine community interest on {{RSL|15 February}} 2013. The poll, which ended {{RSL|1 March}} 2013, decided, among other things, whether an additional [[membership]] fee would be charged for access to the game.{{CiteNews|author = Jagex|title = 2007 - Old School RuneScape... You Vote!|url = http://services.runescape.com/m=news/2007---old-school-runescape-you-vote|newsdate = [[15 February]] [[2013]]|accessdate = 21:52, May 7, 2017 (UTC)}}<!-- Also cited here: http://www.webcitation.org/6qK7JjsKb -->{{CitePoll|url= http://services.runescape.com/m=poll/rs2007-server|poll= Old School RuneScape Servers: Poll Now Live|question= no|polldate= [[15 February]] [[2013]]|name= Poll}}

The poll ended at 00:00 UTC on Friday [[1 March]] [[2013]] with the final tally of votes at 449,351.{{NamedRef|name= Poll}} Although 500,000 votes were needed to allow no additional membership fee, Jagex stated that the first six months of ''Old School RuneScape'' will not have any additional charge. It has since remained open without any additional charge. Currently, ''Old School RuneScape'' is running both [[free-to-play]] and [[pay-to-play]] servers, and players can create new F2P accounts for free without having to pay for membership.

Despite it having originally been stated that servers would take one to two months to be opened following a successful poll, on {{RSL|22 February}} 2013 as part of an Early Access scheme, Jagex opened over 50 ''Old School RuneScape'' servers and gave a month of free ''Old School RuneScape'' membership credit to it to all of those who had voted in the poll. The game quickly saw player counts equalling those of ''RuneScape''.

''Old School RuneScape'' works similarly to ''[[RuneScape Classic]]'' in that players can use their [[main account]]s to access both games. However, any accomplishments, such as [[stats]], [[items]] and [[quests]], are separate and non-transferable. All players, regardless of achievements in other versions of the game, begin ''Old School RuneScape'' on [[Tutorial Island]] with a new character.

''Old School RuneScape'' is rated '''T''' for Teen by the {{wp|Entertainment Software Rating Board}}, '''16''' by {{wp|Pan European Game Information}} committee, and '''Restricted to 15+''' by the {{wp|Australian Classification Board}}.{{CiteGeneral|url=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jagex.oldscape.android|title=Old School RuneScape - Apps on Google Play|accessdate=27 August 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180827052605/https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jagex.oldscape.android|archivedate=27 August 2018}}

==History and release==
2007 servers of ''[[RuneScape]]'' were originally announced in early {{RSL|2013}}. [[Jagex]] allowed players to vote for ''Old School RuneScape'' on a referendum, promising a set of features for every vote mark level reached. The servers were based on a [[August 2007 Archive of RuneScape|backup]] of RuneScape that was created on 10 August 2007.

===Levels===
''Old School RuneScape'' was in four different levels, each with increasing vote requirements. The amount of votes can be seen on [http://services.runescape.com/m=poll/rs2007-server the official vote page]. Regardless of the outcome, any voter will get a free month of Old School RuneScape game time. Although the vote count only reached 449,351 and not 500,000, [[Jagex]] decided not to charge the additional fee of five USD for the first six months (excluding the free month); however, on [[7 June]] [[2013]], they announced that OSRS is here to stay and there will be no additional fee.{{CiteForum|author = Mod Pips|title = Old School here to stay!|url = http://services.runescape.com/m=forum/forums.ws?380,381,76,65448270|postdate = [[7 June]] [[2013]]|accessdate = 10:21, May 8, 2017 (UTC)|name = OSRS Stay}}<!-- Also cached at: http://www.webcitation.org/6qIu7q7nv -->

